data.title: Dave Carter with Tracy Grammer When I Go WSG Tracy Grammer - No Root, No Fruit
data.meta_description: Their career together lasted a brief 5 years before Dave Carter's sudden death in 2002, but the impact of Dave's songs continue to influence and inspire to this day. When I Go was their first record together. Recorded in Tracy's kitchen/ living room, When I go was an introduction to one of America's finest songwriters. Thanks to Tracy for joining me throughout the entire episode!
